    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >与朋友一起更有趣！此游戏不适合单人游戏或与机器人游玩。</h2><br>准备好制造一些骚动并计划你的攻击吧。这些喳喳叫的小鸡们的任务是找回被偷走的蛋，但它们必须躲避愤怒的农夫才能成功。注意，这个农夫一点也不懦弱，他有很多诡计来阻止你。所以磨好你们的喙，伸展你们的翅膀，为终极蛋之旅做好准备吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355860/extras/c7433fe437454ceb952d0b2b2cdbda05.webp?t=1762475937\" width=400 height=52 /></span><br>好了，小鸡小队，听好了！你们要策划一次农场入侵。计划是这样的：潜入农场，抓住那些蛋，然后大胆逃回到鸡舍，路上要躲避农夫的陷阱。是时候向农夫展示谁才是老大了。每一根羽毛都很重要。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355860/extras/c65a88129059925ce93422b8192cf388.poster.avif?t=1762475937\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355860/extras/c65a88129059925ce93422b8192cf388.webm?t=1762475937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355860/extras/c65a88129059925ce93422b8192cf388.mp4?t=1762475937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355860/extras/4e256ad7f3eff646cf55cc6ab4e3b5ab.webp?t=1762475937\" width=400 height=52 /></span><br>你的责任是守卫农场，不惜一切代价击退这些狡猾的小鸡们！谁知道它们又设计了什么阴谋？设置陷阱，封锁窗户，保护那些蛋就像你的生命取决于它们一样。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355860/extras/9266c883242e7a37069d7ee375a5882d.poster.avif?t=1762475937\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355860/extras/9266c883242e7a37069d7ee375a5882d.webm?t=1762475937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355860/extras/9266c883242e7a37069d7ee375a5882d.mp4?t=1762475937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
